project_dir = '/mnt/storageBig8/web-pub/projects/ctDNA/ctDNA_release/'
#--- adding ctdna level into metadata of each scrna object
# primary obj
df <- pobj@meta.data
# join per cell
df <- dplyr::left_join(df, ctdna_cohort)
# now add back with AddMetaData
pobj <- AddMetaData(pobj, metadata = df$ctdna_lev, col.name = "ctdna_lev")
pobj <- AddMetaData(pobj, metadata = df$eoc_code, col.name = "eoc_code")
# add tissue site info
pobj$tissue = stringr::str_match(pobj$sample, "^[^_]+_[piro]\\d?(LN|[A-Z][a-z]+)")[, 2]

Figure 4b: Celltype contribution by patient¶

In [ ]:
#--- cell type distribution by patient and ctdna level groups
options(repr.plot.width = 10, repr.plot.height = 6, align = 'center')

#svg(paste0(project_dir,"/figures/celltype_dist.svg"), 
#  width=7.5, height=4)
pobj@meta.data %>%
    group_by(eoc_code, ctdna_lev, celltypes_updated) %>%
    summarise(cell_count = n(), .groups = "drop") %>%
    group_by(eoc_code, ctdna_lev) %>%
    mutate(total_cells = sum(cell_count)) %>%
    ungroup() %>%
    mutate(frac = (cell_count / total_cells) * 100) %>%
    left_join(ctdna_cohort) %>%   # contains TF variable
    arrange(desc(TF)) %>%
    mutate(eoc_code = factor(eoc_code, levels = unique(eoc_code)))%>% 
    ggplot(aes(x = eoc_code, y = frac, fill = celltypes_updated)) +
    geom_col(width = 0.85) +
    scale_fill_manual(values = cell_cols) +
    labs(
      x = "Patient",
      y = "Proportion of Cells (%)",
      fill = "Cell type"
    ) +
    facet_grid(~factor(ctdna_lev, levels = c('high','med','low')), scales = 'free', space = 'free') +
    theme_bw() +
    theme(
      axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1, size = 13, family = 'Arial'),
      legend.position = "none",
      text = element_text(family = 'Arial', size = 15),
      strip.text = element_text(family = 'Arial', size = 15)
    )

# obtain cancer cells only
cancer_cells <- pobj %>% subset(celltypes_updated == "Ovarian.cancer.cell")

# visualisation for MHCII markers
mhcii = c("HLA-DMA", "HLA-DMB", "HLA-DOA", "HLA-DOB", "HLA-DPA1", "HLA-DPB1", "HLA-DQA1", 
              "HLA-DQA2", "HLA-DQB1", "HLA-DRA", "HLA-DRB1", "HLA-DRB5", "CD74")
cancer = c("PAX8", "WFDC2", "MUC16")

# dotplot
sig_list <- list(MHCII = mhcii,
                  Cancer = cancer)
# Create lookup table for grouping
feature_group <- data.frame(
  feature = unlist(sig_list),
  group = rep(names(sig_list), times = sapply(sig_list, length))
)

cancer_cells$celltype <- factor(cancer_cells$celltypes_updated, levels = c("Ovarian.cancer.cell"))
cancer_cells$ctdna_lev <- factor(cancer_cells$ctdna_lev, levels = c("low","med","high"))

# Run DotPlot with flattened features
p <- DotPlot(cancer_cells, features = feature_group$feature, group.by = "ctdna_lev") 

# Add feature group info to p$data
p$data <- p$data %>%
  left_join(feature_group, by = c("features.plot" = "feature"))

Figure 4d: MHCII signature score¶

In [16]:
# add module scores to cancer cells with UCell
MHC_sets <- list(MHCII=c("HLA-DMA", "HLA-DMB", "HLA-DOA", "HLA-DOB", "HLA-DPA1", "HLA-DPB1", "HLA-DQA1", 
              "HLA-DQA2", "HLA-DQB1", "HLA-DRA", "HLA-DRB1", "HLA-DRB5", "CD74"))

# calculate module scores by UCell
cancer_cells <- UCell::AddModuleScore_UCell(
  cancer_cells,
  features = MHC_sets,
  name = NULL
)

threshold = 0.20 #(Supplementary Figure) #median(cancer_cells$MHCII, na.rm = TRUE)
# cells_df contains: patient_id, ctdna_lev, mhcii (TRUE/FALSE)
patient_mhcii <- cancer_cells@meta.data %>%
  mutate(mhcii_positive = MHCII > threshold) %>%   # binary MHCII+
  group_by(patient, ctdna_lev) %>%
  summarise(
    fraction_mhcii = mean(mhcii_positive, na.rm = TRUE) * 100,
    .groups = "drop"
  )

gene.sets <- list(EMT= c("SMAD3", "COL1A2", "TNC", "SNAI1", "SNAI2"),
              Proliferative=c("PCNA", "CHEK1", "HMGB2", "BRCA2", "FANCI", "POLD1"), 
              Stress=c("JUN", "FOS", "IL6", "TNF", "CXCR4", "SNAI1", "VIM", "GADD45B", "MCL1"),
              Antigen=c("HLA-DPA1", "HLA-DQA1", "HLA-DRA"),
              Differentiation=c("MUC4", "MUC16", "SLPI"),
              Cytokine = c("CXCL1", "CCL20", "IL1R2", "BIRC3", "CDKN2A", "BIK"))

# add module scores to cancer cells with UCell

  cancer_cells,
  features = gene.sets,
  name = NULL

options(repr.plot.width = 10, repr.plot.height = 6, align = 'center')
# Figure: boxplot of signature scores by ctdna level
#svg(paste0(project_dir,"/figures/main/4e_sig_score_ctdna_level_boxplot.svg"), width=8, height=4)
cancer_cells@meta.data %>%
  group_by(patient, ctdna_lev) %>%
  dplyr::summarise(mean_prolif = mean(Proliferative, na.rm = TRUE),
                  mean_EMT = mean(EMT, na.rm = TRUE),
                  mean_stress = mean(Stress,na.rm = TRUE),
                  mean_antigen = mean(Antigen, na.rm=TRUE),
                  mean_cytokine = mean(Cytokine, na.rm=TRUE),
                  mean_diff = mean(Differentiation),
                  mean_mhcii = mean(MHCII, na.rm=TRUE))  %>%
  as.data.frame() %>%
  tidyr::gather(key = "signature", value = "score", 
                mean_prolif:mean_diff) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = factor(ctdna_lev, levels=c('low','med','high')), y = score)) +
  geom_boxplot(aes(color=factor(ctdna_lev, levels=c('low','med','high'))), 
              show.legend = F, width = .4) +
  geom_jitter(aes(color=factor(ctdna_lev, levels=c('low','med','high'))),
              width = 0.2, alpha = 0.6, show.legend = FALSE) +
  scale_color_manual(values=c("low"="#cc3333", "med"="#339933", "high"="#003399")) +
  facet_wrap(~factor(signature, levels = c('mean_prolif','mean_EMT','mean_stress','mean_antigen','mean_cytokine','mean_diff'), 
  labels = c('Proliferation','EMT-associated','Stress-associated',"Antigen presentation", "Cytokine","Differentiation")), 
  scales = "free_y", ncol = 3) +
  labs(color='', x='', y = 'Signature score') +
  theme_classic() +
  theme(axis.text = element_text(family = 'Arial', size = 15),
        axis.title = element_text(family = 'Arial', size = 16),
        plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, family = 'Arial', size = 16),
        strip.text = element_text(family = 'Arial', size = 13))

# M1 and M2 related score calculation
M1_genes = c("CCL19", "TNF", "CCL5")
M2_genes = c("CD163", "MRC1", "CCL18", "CCL13")

myeloid_obj <- UCell::AddModuleScore_UCell(
  myeloid_obj,
  features = list(M1 = M1_genes,
                  M2 = M2_genes),
  name = NULL
)

plot_df <- myeloid_obj@meta.data |>
  group_by(eoc_code, ctdna_lev) |>
  summarise(
    mean_M1 = mean(M1, na.rm = TRUE),
    mean_M2 = mean(M2, na.rm = TRUE),
    .groups = "drop"
  ) |>
  tidyr::pivot_longer(
    cols = c(mean_M1, mean_M2),
    names_to = "TAM_type",
    values_to = "score"
  )
